issue.title: fixed slider to appear and be properly formatted
issue.body: Fixed the slider to be properly formatted and appear under the listing view. The main issue was that the css wasn't being imported, the second biggest was the slider being two small in terms of width. This css fix was easy with an import, the width issue is hardcoded into the slider.
